{"tid":911873,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU Team是怎麼看IU的？吐露她的暖心細節，感激得哽咽落淚...","createTime":"2018-11-22T08:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T06:57:24.000Z","uid":34643,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa824080b12cd715e9befcbc29c29f11ff525506","tid":911873,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_a5de10b36fe5fd57e79c2f5eab61d667/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-21/111454-678893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_a5de10b36fe5fd57e79c2f5eab61d667%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-21%2F111454-678893.jpg&h=b9d4ec7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n演唱會上的這段VCR是催淚彈啊，看完也許你也會流淚...<br />\n<br />\n在近日舉辦的IU演唱會上，放了IU Team出鏡的VCR， IU的經紀人、樂隊、伴舞、服裝師等都說出了自己對IU的想法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9d28dafcc3a9d5e3aafd25ac09d9c91b/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-21/111454-678896.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9d28dafcc3a9d5e3aafd25ac09d9c91b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-21%2F111454-678896.jpg&h=a0125536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伴舞：「IU在耶誕節時，給每位伴舞都親手寫了封信，內容還很長，還一一傳達了。 」<br />\n<br />\n伴舞：「IU在小事上也經常稱讚，多虧了IU，我們的自信心也大大上升了。 」<br />\n<br />\n伴舞： 「實話說，工作時對伴舞、樂隊和其他工作人員都很開心地問候真是不常見的事情。 她是創造了IU Team的一等功臣。 」<br />\n<br />\n團隊指導：「我總是很抱歉，可她一直說沒關係，總說不是我的錯。 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_93fa2b067455b578e9ea57a1165f1b50/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-21/111454-678895.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_93fa2b067455b578e9ea57a1165f1b50%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-21%2F111454-678895.jpg&h=5a3d9824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n服裝師：「Chat-Shire巡演時，知恩自己很辛苦。 她安可時唱了《秘密》，我那時心痛得哭得很厲害。 」<br />\n<br />\n另外一位服裝師也說著說著就哭了，髮型師更是還沒開口就哽咽了：「很感謝她一直為我們著想...」<br />\n<br />\n一位經紀人：「以前在去英國的飛機上，和IU說過想在十周年的時候能在體操競技場開唱，沒想到真的實現了。 」<br />\n<br />\n▼更多工作人員的評價，可看下方的中字影片：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gl0wX4HPJmk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgl0wX4HPJmk&d=qAGctaA1C1X%2F6UEGp%2F687LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=299045b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gl0wX4HPJmk</a><br />\n<br />\nIU對自己團隊的熱心照料是人盡皆知的，和IU Team的感情深厚。"},{"pid":"ebb4618466811854ecc71c371ec6dfddbdc21ac4","tid":911873,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"韓泡塑化雞流膠淚"},{"pid":"6149a31a924845f0acec6d09ff4344cde9d55f92","tid":911873,"uid":89660,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"ebb4618466811854ecc71c371ec6dfddbdc21ac4","tid":911873,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"韓泡塑化雞流膠淚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:11:37.000Z","msg":"收下你把閪口啦仆街"},{"pid":"e5bee8bbac407f3498e3c4e6c086b24de0fe3d5c","tid":911873,"uid":213470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"播得出黎梗係咁講啦, 唔通唱衰佢咩<br />\n利申: IU世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0d46238cbff5dd920898f25b91438b4ec498e5","tid":911873,"uid":72076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82fc1744554c0f0a71bb0ea13276c7eee92b7cc","tid":911873,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:53:27.000Z","msg":"IU曾經給結婚的IU team的員工送過一輛奔馳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://ss0.baidu.com/6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=1948079640,3931573718&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fss0.baidu.com%2F6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fit%2Fu%3D1948079640%2C3931573718%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJP